Description:
The Podium is Within Reach!
Located in the award winning Watergate residential complex, this low rise home among the tree tops has the most tranquil outlook around. Cosy and private, this apartment will suit a buyer looking for peace and quiet.
As you enter the apartment you will appreciate the stylish kitchen with white stone benchtop and white cabinetry. Stainless steel appliances include a gas stove top, oven and a dishwasher.
Open plan dining and living area adjoins the full length balcony set along lush greenery.
To the left of the apartment are two large bedrooms. Both bedrooms with mirrored BIR’s, main includes ensuite with 2nd bedroom sharing the central tiled bathroom.
Additional features include ducted reverse cycle heating and cooling, secured carpark, onsite manager with security entrance, floor to ceiling double glazed windows and cross flow ventilation.
Recreational facilities consist of a fantastic 3 lane heated swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a residents lounge.
Centrally located in the heart of the Docklands makes it convenience plus. Walking distance to Woolworths, Australia Post Office, Library at the Dock, Southern Cross Station, superb cafes and eateries. Free Tram Zoned, easy access to the freeway and a short stroll into Melbourne CBD.

Great Value Apartment Will Never Last Long!
Strategically positioned at the Batman's Hill precinct in Docklands, on the 1st floor within the prestigious 'Watergate' building is this superb apartment in the South Tower featuring an open plan living area.
Located near the business precinct of Docklands between Collins and Bourke Streets and within close proximity to the Southern Cross Station, Etihad Stadium, ANZ, Myer and NAB headquarters; the location is right where you need it to be.

This magnificent apartment will appeal to the most discerning owner occupier and investor alike.

Description:
Unforgettable Views From The Exclusive 'Harbour 1'
Set in the magnificent 'Harbour 1' complex which is just metres away from the tranquil Victoria Harbour, this premier two bedroom, two bathroom residence defines immaculate and uber-stylish Docklands living with views to truly envy.
A clever floorplan and wonderful water vistas define this 20th floor beauty, with the memorable views best appreciated from the generous undercover balcony. The central living zone is open yet versatile enough to give you dedicated spaces for both lounge and dining. Meanwhile, the kitchen looks out over the central area and delivers plenty of bench space made from quality stone as well as stainless steel appliances.
The bedrooms are positioned on opposite corners of the apartment for blissful privacy and includes the large master retreat which has a share of the harbour views along with dual built-in robes and a ensuite. Other apartment extras include a gorgeous main bathroom, study nook with desk, European laundry, central heating and cooling, intercom entry, and 2 secure car spaces.

Description:
Dynamic Location & Privileged Position!
Docklands would have to be one of Melbourne’s most Dynamic and Evolving suburbs. With key attractions including Etihad Stadium and the Melbourne Star. It has also secured Large Local and International Corporations as residents. Completing the dynamic is approximately 10,000 residential residents who also call Docklands home!
Positioned on the fringe of Melbourne CBD and The Docklands, the property is conveniently located and also only a few minutes to Southern Cross Station, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Southwarf DFO and of course an abundance of shops, cafes, bars and restaurants. Its also located within the free tram zone, providing convenient access to the property and surrounding amenities.
This impressive and light-filled Docklands apartment is well perched on the 9th floor. Offering 2 spacious bedrooms, each with built in robes, a large kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Other luxury features include double glazed windows, heating and cooling, and a large private balcony, which is perfect for entertaining. A modern building features security access entry and resort style facilities including an outdoor swimming pool and fully equipped Gym for resident use.
Whether you are looking for a place to call home or a securely leased investment opportunity, I look forward to speaking with you and seeing you at one of our weekly open homes.

Description:
WATERFRONT MODERN LUXURY!
Sophisticated waterfront luxury and breathtaking views of the Yarra River, Point Park, and the iconic Melbourne skyline make this two bedroom, two bathroom, north orientated apartment a highly sought-after prize.
Located on the 21st floor of the stylish Yarra Point complex, this spacious pad measuring 119 sqm (approx.) showcases a dedicated lounge and dining area, along with a designer kitchen featuring stone island bench, terrific storage and gas Miele appliances including a dishwasher.
The exceptional private balcony will be ideal in the warmer months for alfresco meals as you soak in the astonishing city and river vistas, while bedrooms, both with BIRs and contemporary bathrooms with large showers and vanities.
Further enjoying ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to building facilities including a gymnasium, BBQ area & playground and heated pool, this retreat is in close proximity to South Wharf restaurants, DFO shopping, Etihad Stadium, CBD attractions, and public transport.

Description:
Flawless Tower 5 Excellence with Elevated Harbour and City Views
Graced with outstanding custom upgrades and impeccable views of the scenic Yarra’s Edge marina and the iconic city skyline, this unprecedented two bedroom, two bathroom apartment sits on the 28th floor of ‘Tower 5’ and promises magnificent Yarra’s Edge living.
Quality craftsmanship and superb attention to detail will get your attention immediately. A generous and open plan lounge and dining zone has a fantastic north-east orientation, with this central zone effortlessly flowing out to the huge undercover balcony which takes in views of the resplendent river and city plus Port Phillip Bay.
The kitchen boasts upgraded marble countertops including a sizeable island bench, Ilve and Qasair stainless steel appliances, and integrated Liebherr fridge and freezer. The master retreat is an amazing space all on its own, with a large walk-in robe, beautiful spa ensuite, and its own access to the generous balcony.
Further take advantage of a 2nd bedroom with a built-in robe, central marble bathroom with a European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, motorised blinds, C-bus lighting system, Bose surround-sound system, full height pivot doors to bedrooms, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Enjoy terrific nearby South Wharf attractions including DFO shopping and restaurants/bars including The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard. You’re also near Crown Casino with world class restaurants and entertainment, CBD, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
By Appointment Only
Situated on the top floor of the exclusive Watergate complex, this unrivalled three bedroom, two bathroom Docklands stunner is an immaculate apartment offering flawless attention to detail, marvelous modern style, and brilliant living space.
This 18th floor property makes a statement right from the very start, as you open the door into the expansive lounge and dining zone delivering with lofty ceilings and windows allowing for outstanding natural light and views. This central space also has a wonderful feature wall fitted with Italian Porcelanosa tiles, exquisite floating shelving, and a wallpaper OLED TV (65 inch size, only 4mm thick).
The adjoining kitchen is as sophisticated as it is elegant, with a Kai Byok-designed pendant light hanging over the deluxe stone benchtop. Stainless steel Fisher & Paykel and Miele appliances, soft-closing drawers, an integrated fridge and freezer, and a 2nd butler’s benchtop ideal for meal preparation are other amazing kitchen highlights.
The master bedroom comes with a sleek private ensuite with heated floor tiles, WIR and access to a balcony, while the 2nd bedroom with a BIR has entry to the dual access feature bathroom complete with under floor heating. This bathroom absolutely dazzles with a sublime freestanding bath and rain shower which enjoys a full window allowing for amazing views and terrific natural light.
The study has custom shelving and sliding doors meaning you can enjoy an open or private home office experience, with this room easily converted into a 3rd bedroom if you so choose. The main balcony area features breathtaking views of Docklands Park, Port Phillip Bay, Yarra River, and down to South Wharf, meanwhile further benefit from a laundry, ducted heating and cooling, touch lights, video intercom entry, and 2 secure car spaces. You also have access to a pool, sauna, and gym.
Love the popular Victoria Harbour precinct which is moments to great places to dine and catch up with friends including The Hof Downtown, The Nixon Hotel, and Ginger Leaf Thai Restaurant just to name a few. You also have Etihad Stadium metres from your door which is a dream for footy fans, while you’re close to Docklands Park, The Hub @Docklands, Bourke Street cafes, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Myles Johansson on 0448 031 716 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
The Exciting Wave of Change
From humble beginnings, the Docklands has transformed into a precinct many now call home.
The gateway to the Docklands from Flinders Street, The Village Docklands is set in a prime position. Close to South Wharf and the South Western corner of the Melbourne CBD, you can easily travel in all directions.
Located in V1 Village Docklands residential complex, this fabulous 2 bedroom apartment, with a flow through design, is the ideal residence as it offers a total of 108sqm which includes a living area of 91sqm.
Open plan dining, living area adjoins a fabulous Winter Garden with louvres.
Galley style kitchen with integrated stainless steel appliances including gas stove top, oven and dish washer.
Large main bedroom with stylish ensuite and built in robes. 2nd bedroom, also with built in robes, shares the central fully tiled bathroom with bathtub.
Features of the apartment
• Reverse cycle heating and cooling
• Secure under cover car park
• Twin balconies, North and South facing
Other features include
• Onsite manager
• Security entrance
• Covered Swimming pool
Within the free tram zone, the stop is virtually at your front door and coupled with the Southern Cross Station, transportation is a breeze in and out.
Fabulous eateries along Flinders Wharf or stroll a little further to enjoy the Crown Entertainment Complex.

91m²

Promising an array of stunning highlights including a wealth of sensational internal space, refined and contemporary style and breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour and CBD, this brilliant 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in the Conder complex is the ultimate Docklands experience!
In a building designed by the award-winning Fender Katsalidis, this 6th floor residence does all the little things right, from bright full windows, quality tapware, premium carpet and sleek stone surfaces. The central living and dining zone is a wonderful display of spacious open living, with this huge area having amazing views of Victoria Harbour and the city skyline through the large and light windows.
The expansive central zone has direct access to the undercover balcony which is the perfect vantage point to soak in the harbour views. The kitchen displays modern class along with an island bench and stainless steel Miele & Bosch appliances, meanwhile the three fantastic bedrooms all have built-in robe storage including the master bedroom which comes with a chic private ensuite.
Other property features include a central bathroom, separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, storage cage, two secure car spaces and access to the indoor pool, gym and outdoor grassed recreation area. Enjoy all the delights of the relaxed NewQuay Precinct where you can dine at superb nearby restaurants including Fish Bar, The Conder restaurant and Renzo’s Bar Café Italiano just to name a few. You’re also near Etihad Stadium, the newly redeveloped District Docklands and trams across Melbourne.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Harbour Views From Arkley Will Delight **Under Offer**
Beautifully presented on the ninth floor of the renowned Arkley building the immaculate views over Victoria Harbour, the Etihad Precinct and to the city skyline will delight. Arkley is located in the heart of NewQuay just a short walk to the undercover shopping precinct, waterfront cafes and restaurants and Free Tram to the CBD. The spacious living and dining area opens to a private balcony with ample room for entertaining, outdoor eating and relaxed waterfront living. The large master suite incorporates a sizeable study area and immaculate ensuite. The impressive second bedroom is serviced by a large bathroom including separate shower and bath. A superb modern kitchen with ample bench space, separate laundry, air-conditioning, two undercover carparks, large storage cage, secure access and resident enjoyment of heated pool, gym and spa complement an outstanding Docklands lifestyle. Inspection a must.

Description:
WATER VIEWS WITHOUT THE PRICE TAG
Delivering spectacular views is this large Lacrosse apartment on La Trobe Street.
Comprising of 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1 car space, this Docklands dwelling possesses space and elegance, as well as floor to ceiling windows that present a stunning vista from the south east of Melbourne all the way to Victoria Harbour.
The generous open plan living area comes with a stylish kitchen complete with dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, concealed fridge, and stone bench-top. The large master bedroom comes with built-in-robes, and a chic, modern en-suite. The second bedroom is also generous in size, and includes plenty of storage with its built in robes. Both bedrooms have loads of natural light. The central bathroom completes this fab package with its clean, contemporary finishes, ample storage, and euro-laundry.
A feature through-out this inner city pad is loads of storage, and is rounded out by central heating/cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry.
Typical of modern apartment living, additional facilities for residents include a fully equipped gym and heated outdoor pool. With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
North-Facing Forge Oasis is a Stylish Standout
With an enviable northerly aspect that allows for truly special views of the memorable city skyline, this brand new two bedroom, two bathroom apartment in the Forge complex is one of the best opportunities in the Yarra’s Edge precinct.
With contemporary grace and a considered floorplan which makes the most of the space and views, this 10th floor apartment will have widespread appeal. Sizeable and open lounge and dining includes a dazzling stone kitchen featuring elegant cabinetry and Smeg stainless steel appliances.
There are three access points out to the balcony (from central living and both bedrooms), with this wonderful alfresco zone brilliant to soak in the CBD and Yarra River views as well as out to the rest of the Docklands. Both bedrooms are equipped with built-in robes including the master haven which also delivers an ensuite. Enjoy a sumptuous central bathroom, concealed laundry, heating and cooling, video intercom and a secure car space. Residents also has access to the exclusive Wharf Club with gym, pool and café as well as a private kitchen/dining room and cinema.
Walk to South Wharf promenade with restaurants and bars including Citizen Café and Bar, Melbourne Public, Bangpop, and Munich Brauhaus. You’re also near the Victoria Harbour precinct, Crown Entertainment Complex with world class restaurants, Port Melbourne and South Melbourne attractions, and Southern Cross Station.
